23:44.643 --> 23:45.993
To what, Richard,

23:46.331 --> 23:48.376
arm-wrestling, a spelling bee?

23:49.088 --> 23:51.971
When I was at Oxford
on my Rhodes scholarship,

23:52.708 --> 23:54.633
